info.description: A heavenly combination of chocolate and vanilla married together with chocolate chips and ribbon. A feisty ribbon twirling its way through this chocolate chip loaded chocolate and vanilla ice cream scoop. This ice cream is as enticing as they come!(contains milk & soy)

info.name: Dutch Chocolate Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Tempting chocolate ice cream with a distinct hint of cocoa. The mother of every chocolate ice cream creation of ours.

info.name: Belgian Bliss Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Rich chocolate ice cream with hidden treasures of dark chocolate cookies, hugged by a caramel ribbon. This delectable chocolate delight is like no other! sit back and enjoy this rich belgian bliss ice cream.

info.name: Chocolate Almond Praline Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Praline coated almonds peeping out of dark chocolate ice cream (contains milk & tree nuts (almond)

info.name: Mint Milk Chocolate Chips Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: An ice cream that tells the mint and chocolate love story like no other. This classic ice cream is a marriage of mint and milk chocolate pieces.

info.name: Bavarian Chocolate Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Rich chocolate based ice cream adorned with chocolate pieces and cashew nut crispies. If it's bavarian chocolate flavour then it's gotta be sinful and intensely indulgent. Throw in a bit of crunch and you've got a truly divine chocolate ice cream treat.

info.name: Chocolate Mousse Royale Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Mischievous chocolate chips playing peekaboo with frozen chocolate mousse dessert. There's no such thing as too much chocolate is there? how about you triple up on this cool chocolate chip mousse ice cream with a chocolate waffle cone?

info.name: Gold Medal Ribbon Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: A heavenly medley of vanilla and chocolate, embraced by a caramel ribbon. This vanilla and chocolate combo is our dream team! a thick, deep caramel ribbon intertwines the two flavours together in perfection.

info.name: Ferrero Moments Mousse Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: A rich hazelnut chocolate mousse ice cream swirled with chocolate ribbon and adorned with crushed ferrero moments. A moment of bliss

info.name: Naughty Nutella Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Heavenly nutella ice cream made with velvety nutella paste and premium chocolate. Get nutty!

info.name: Vanilla Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Not quite like a plain jane, this is a rich, dense vanilla ice cream that you'll recommend to friends. Seriously creamy, seriously tasty, a lot can happen over a vanilla ice cream! (contains milk)

info.name: Roasted Californian Almond Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Vanilla ice cream with caramel ribbon and almond praline. We've put together two classics flavours with a caramel ribbon stitching them together. This almond praline gold proves that sometime old is truly gold! (contains milk & tree nuts)

info.name: Splish Splash Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Celestial ice cream with a dark blue raspberry and light blueberry embrace. This delectable blue raspberry and blueberry ice cream scoop with leave you feeling blue. The right kind of blue! (contains milk)

info.name: Cotton Candy Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Perky pink, purple and childhood coloured cotton candy flavoured ice cream. We're happy to let you know that we have fulfilled every child's wish of cotton candy ice cream.

info.name: Honey Nut Crunch Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Ice cream with rich caramel and honey praline almonds. Honey, it's nutty, it's crunchy and it's delightful. What are you waiting for? get yourself a load of this honey nut crunch ice cream. (contains milk & tree nuts)

info.name: Roasted Coffee Creme Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Luscious ice cream with freshly ground coffee. This cool coffee flavoured ice cream will delight all coffee lovers out there! (contains milk)

info.name: Hop Scotch Butterscotch Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: With a butterscotch base, this ice cream has cashew crunch along with an enticing butterscotch ribbon. Stop drooling, start clicking! our butterscotch ice cream is calling out to you! (contains milk & tree nuts)

info.name: Cookies 'N Cream Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Classic vanilla ice cream loaded with sweet oreo cookie crumble. Classic never goes out of style!

info.name: Lotus Biscoff Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Biscoff flavoured ice cream with lotus biscoff pieces and a caramel ribbon. Unexpectedly delightful!

info.name: Very Berry Strawberry Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Sublime strawberry ice cream with real strawberry pieces. This strawberry ice cream is a childhood favourite. Scrap that actually, it's an all time favourite! (contains milk)

info.name: Banana 'N Strawberry Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Ice cream with real banana and strawberries with strawberry ribbon. This banana and strawberry ice cream combination has stood the test of time. You simply cannot go wrong with this delicious ice cream.

info.name: Alphonso Mango Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Delicious alphonso mango based ice cream made with juicy, real mango pulp. Just go for this aam-azing mango ice cream! (contains milk)

info.name: Fruit Overload Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Orange flavoured ice cream adorned with exotic fruit chunks and jelly. This fruity delight is truly delicious! get a load of this fruit overload ice cream!

info.name: Black Currant Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Black currant ice cream with real black currant and raisins. This flavoured sweet treat is a universal favourite!

info.name: Shooting Star Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Your wish for a quirky, vibrant ice cream just came true. A combination of blueberry and vanilla ice cream swirled with a refreshing cherry ribbon and loaded with coloured sugar strands and popping candy. Super fun, super delicious.

info.name: Blueberry 'N White Chocolate Ice Cream (Tub)
info.description: Exotic blend of white chocolate ice cream with sweet blueberries. A purple scoop of joy!

info.name: Salted Caramel Crunch Gelato (Tub)
info.description: Silky salted caramel gelato loaded with golden, crunchy honeycomb pieces. Crafted the italian way

info.name: Mango & Cream Gelato (Tub)
info.description: Luscious cream gelato with sweet mango chunks. Taste the italian sunshine.

info.name: Blueberry Cheesecake Gelato (Tub)
info.description: Creamy cheesecake gelato swirled with exotic blueberries and new york style cheesecake bits, made the italian way

info.name: Cotton Candy Burst Gelato (Tub)
info.description: Tri-coloured cotton candy gelato with popping candy! a burst of italian fun

info.name: Chocolate & Roasted Hazelnut Gelato (Tub)
info.description: Luxuriously smooth chocolate with roasted hazelnut crunch, an italian affair

info.name: Variety Pack
info.description: The variety pack is a delightful assortment of 6 small ice cream scoops of your choice, perfect for sharing with friends and family. Share the scoops. Share the happyness!
